{"text_id":132051,"tokens":["In"," the"," ongoing"," debate"," about"," whether"," summer"," assignments"," should"," be"," student","-","designed"," or"," teacher","-","assigned",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," teacher","-","assigned"," projects"," are"," more"," effective"," in"," keeping"," students"," mentally"," active"," during"," their"," summer"," break","."," While"," student","-","designed"," assignments"," may"," offer"," certain"," benefits",","," such"," as"," promoting"," creativity"," and"," independence",","," they"," also"," come"," with"," limitations"," that"," can"," hinder"," a"," student","'","s"," academic"," growth",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," main"," advantages"," of"," student","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," is"," the"," opportunity"," for"," creativity","."," Allowing"," students"," to"," choose"," their"," own"," topics"," and"," design"," their"," own"," projects"," can"," foster"," a"," sense"," of"," ownership"," and"," enthusiasm","."," For"," instance",","," a"," student"," interested"," in"," photography"," may"," decide"," to"," document"," their"," summer"," travels"," through"," a"," photo"," journal","."," This"," individualized"," approach"," can"," lead"," to"," increased"," engagement"," and"," motivation"," as"," students"," have"," the"," chance"," to"," explore"," their"," own"," interests"," and"," passions",".","\n\n","However",","," the"," drawbacks"," of"," student","-","designed"," assignments"," must"," not"," be"," overlooked","."," First"," and"," foremost",","," there"," is"," a"," risk"," of"," students"," not"," challenging"," themselves"," adequately","."," When"," left"," to"," their"," own"," devices",","," some"," students"," may"," choose"," projects"," that"," are"," too"," easy"," or"," familiar",","," resulting"," in"," minimal"," intellectual"," growth","."," Additionally",","," without"," a"," standardized"," framework",","," it"," becomes"," challenging"," for"," teachers"," to"," assess"," and"," provide"," meaningful"," feedback"," on"," student"," work","."," This"," lack"," of"," accountability"," may"," lead"," to"," a"," superficial"," approach"," towards"," the"," assignments",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," teacher","-","assigned"," summer"," assignments"," provide"," a"," structured"," framework"," that"," ensures"," academic"," rigor"," and"," intellectual"," development","."," Teachers"," possess"," the"," expertise"," to"," design"," assignments"," that"," align"," with"," the"," curriculum"," and"," challenge"," students"," appropriately","."," For"," instance",","," a"," literature"," teacher"," may"," assign"," a"," reading"," list"," that"," includes"," complex"," and"," thought","-","provoking"," books",","," pushing"," students"," to"," expand"," their"," literary"," analysis"," skills","."," Furthermore",","," these"," assignments"," allow"," teachers"," to"," assess"," students","'"," progress"," and"," provide"," feedback"," for"," improvement",","," contributing"," to"," their"," overall"," growth",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," student","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," may"," promote"," creativity"," and"," autonomy",","," the"," drawbacks"," of"," potential"," lack"," of"," challenge"," and"," accountability"," outweigh"," these"," benefits","."," Teacher","-","assigned"," assignments"," not"," only"," ensure"," academic"," rigor"," but"," also"," allow"," for"," meaningful"," assessment"," and"," feedback","."," Therefore",","," I"," firmly"," believe"," that"," teacher","-","assigned"," projects"," are"," more"," effective"," in"," keeping"," students"," mentally"," active"," during"," their"," summer"," break","."," By"," striking"," a"," balance"," between"," structure"," and"," creativity",","," students"," can"," engage"," in"," assignments"," that"," foster"," both"," intellectual"," growth"," and"," personal"," expression","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo